<Author>znieto
<Content>Good location, right at the heart of Mexico City 10 min walk to Palacio de bella artes, 15 min to Touristo bus, 10 min to Zocalo, and 15 min to St Juan market. Room clean and size is good enough. The perimeter around the hotel is not the best, but ones you are inside the hotel every thing change. Staff is very friendly. Reception was very helpful when it came to requests.I would definitely recommend staying here. 
