<Author>KINGKONG3
<Content>Convinient and clean We stayed at this hotel as part of a tour, so I can't comment on prices. However, this hotel was clean, comfortable and convenient for the Zocalo and subway stations.There's a lift, Internet access, and the room was dark and quiet - ideal following a hectic day in the city.The area felt safe, and there was a 24 hour convenience store a block away which was handy.Certainly, if I returned to Mexico City I would have no problem with staying here again - it was cheap and cheerful! 
